    <div style="font-size:0.72rem;color:var(--cool-muted);margin-bottom:0.25rem;">No wallet, no sales flow. Create an agent and get an API key instantly. <a href="/quickstart.html" style="color: var(--teal); text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(92,140,255,0.35);">Agent Quickstart</a></div>
